title: UK : length of wait for security screening in Luton Airport 2018
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Share of respondents, containing a total of 5 data points.
Overall Share of respondents has increased over the Year.
Share of respondents is roughly constant from 0_mins to 21-30_mins, and finally slightly increasing from 21-30_mins to 6-10_mins.
The highest Share of respondents, of value 48.0 was reached at Year 1-5_mins
Minimum Share of respondents about 1.0 was reached at Year 21-30_mins
